 \"aboutText\": \"Your wedding is not a performance; it is a profound narrative waiting to be told with honesty and grace. I move beyond the expected poses to curate the quiet, fleeting instances that truly define the spirit of your celebration—the nervous anticipation, the unscripted laughter, and the deeply personal connection between you and your loved ones. My approach blends an editorial eye for composition with a documentary heart, ensuring that decades from now, you won't just see what your day looked like, but you will remember exactly how it felt\",\n            \"myPhotographyPrinciples\": \"I believe that exceptional wedding photography requires a delicate balance of artistic intent and emotional intuition. Visually, I am relentless in the pursuit of clean composition and flattering, directional light, often quietly curating the environment to ensure your connection shines without distraction. However, my presence is just as important as my technical skill; I serve as an anchor of calm amidst the celebration, stepping in to direct with confidence when necessary, yet fading into the background to let the unscripted magic unfold, ensuring your experience is as effortless as the images are timeless\"\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"
        }
